name: Photo Affect Measure
description: Data collected from a single session on the PAM App.
csv_mapper: [ {"field": "header.participant_id", "displayName": "Participant ID"}, {"field": "header.participant_label", "displayName": "Participant Label"}, {"field": "body.effective_time_frame.date_time", "displayName": "Date", "cellFilter": "date:'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm'"}, {"field": "body.mood", "displayName": "Mood"}, {"field": "body.negative-affect", "displayName": "Negative Affect"}, {"field": "body.positive-affect", "displayName": "Positive Affect"}, {"field": "body.affect_valence", "displayName": "Affect Valence"}, {"field": "body.affect_arousal", "displayName": "Affect Arousal"} ]

name: Mobility Daily Summary
description: Daily computed summaries based on activity data.
csv_mapper: [ {"field": "header.participant_id", "displayName": "Participant ID"}, {"field": "header.participant_label", "displayName": "Participant Label"}, {"field": "body.date", "displayName": "Date"}, {"field": "body.device", "displayName": "Source"}, {"field": "body.active_time_in_seconds", "displayName": "Active Time (seconds)"}, {"field": "body.walking_distance_in_km", "displayName": "Walking Distance (km)"}, {"field": "body.steps", "displayName": "Step Count"}, {"field": "body.geodiameter_in_km", "displayName": "Geodiameter (km)"}, {"field": "body.max_gait_speed_in_meter_per_second", "displayName": "Max Gait Speed (m/s)"}, {"field": "body.leave_home_time", "displayName": "Left Home Time", "cellFilter": "date:'HH:mm:ss'"}, {"field": "body.return_home_time", "displayName": "Return Home Time", "cellFilter": "date:'HH:mm:ss'"}, {"field": "body.time_not_at_home_in_seconds", "displayName": "Time Not at Home (seconds)"}, {"field": "body.coverage", "displayName": "Coverage"} ]
